I'd like to confim your belief.  My experience indicates that kernels
2.2.10 and above are NOT stable.  They last from several minutes to
hours on my servers.  I've got a pretty diverse set of machines and
NONE of them are stable above 2.2.9.
-- 
Jeffrey Hundstad
